Package: BiostatTools
Type: Package
Title: Functions for basic exploratory data analysis.
Version: 0.1.2
Author: Albert Sorribas
Maintainer: <albert.sorribas@udl.cat>
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), tidyverse, compareGroups, UsingR, DescTools, 
        ggpubr,questionr,formattable,epitools,kableExtra, descr, questionr
Description: Obtain formated crosstables, bar plots with simultaneous confidence intervals,
    and other useful tools for dealing with tables and means. The goal is to offer easy
    tools for exploratory data analysis.
License: GNU
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
